data.description: If you are looking for a home close to Watts Bar lake, then look no further. This 3 BR and 2 BA home will wow you when you walk in the door with the large open living room, hardwood floors, spacious kitchen that features custom built cabinets, walk in pantry, and large dining area. The home is located minutes from the Spring City Marina/Restaurant with a year-round boat launch and fishing pier.  You will enjoy relaxing on the front covered porch where you can see beautiful Watts Bar Lake or sit on back deck overlooking the peaceful private yard/fenced. High speed internet available. Schedule your private showing today.
